Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,703)}我沒有想到會這麼順利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.82,PS2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(796,83)\frz4.986}二瀨文緒
